{"tid":1280922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次人如果真係無事就好，但今次過去，邊個自殺都唔係同路人！","createTime":"2019-07-03T06:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T14:17:03.000Z","uid":32051,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"212937c18055298cef0b2ff83f9e1dfc86f4a16c","tid":1280922,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:29:43.000Z","msg":"立帖為證<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無同路人會搞到咁多人擔心你大半日<br />\n同路人係互相扶持<br />\n唔該唔開心請搵身邊朋友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地已經承受唔起再有人自殺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊個再自殺，即係傷害所有同路人。<br />\n如果你自殺，請記住你比警犬對同路人造成更大傷害<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以唔好死！</span>"},{"pid":"5a5eb38b7f6683f1ef2d6412f36734d22d22ec96","tid":1280922,"uid":258972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f1c898d9b92e62d4a69f219a280e63e3802b3528","tid":1280922,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:31:53.000Z","msg":"唔好再用生命去令同路人擔心"},{"pid":"0107069a547ddb778b06f2bdbf3bc6b595dcfde2","tid":1280922,"uid":250877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:02:16.000Z","msg":"推，明白大家都有種無力感，真係好唔開心就搵同聲同氣既人傾，一齊鬧出尼，將負面情緒發洩晒出尼，唔好自己諗埋一邊"},{"pid":"1d8e7ed61b1b80b750f6d515883d2bebc4d240a4","tid":1280922,"uid":103613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:03:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b821d7559af6a2c0f68ef7facf66226cc50258d6","tid":1280922,"uid":103613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:09:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5054b7a5dcbcf043072ab2739e9f22944bc1941","tid":1280922,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:17:03.000Z","msg":"邊個自殺，邊個就唔係同路人"}]}